This example requires Mocha, if not already installed:

  sudo gem install mocha

The first example tests using stubs, to run the tests:

  ruby test_using_stubs.rb

When successfully run it should report 1 test, 1 assertion and 0 failures.

The second example tests expectations using mocks, to run the tests:

  ruby test_using_mocha.rb

When successfully run it should report 1 test, 6 assertion and 0 failures.
